Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.03,Default,Man B,0,0,0,,{\be1}Bác ơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.03,Default,Man B,0,0,0,,{\be1}Cho Leone một ly!
